{"words":[{"word":"te","count":8},{"word":"class","count":6},{"word":"href","count":4},{"word":"data","count":3},{"word":"oh","count":3},{"word":"help","count":3},{"word":"roya","count":3},{"word":"six","count":3},{"word":"calm","count":2},{"word":"good","count":2},{"word":"maybe","count":2},{"word":"lose","count":2},{"word":"huh","count":2},{"word":"professor","count":2},{"word":"mornye","count":2},{"word":"i've","count":2},{"word":"wait","count":2},{"word":"today","count":2},{"word":"find","count":2},{"word":"horns","count":2},{"word":"wear","count":2},{"word":"solisylum","count":2},{"word":"heliodic","count":2},{"word":"mam","count":2},{"word":"i'd","count":2},{"word":"maja","count":1},{"word":"stopped","count":1},{"word":"shut","count":1},{"word":"force","count":1},{"word":"shutdown","count":1},{"word":"i'll","count":1},{"word":"thesis","count":1},{"word":"somebody","count":1},{"word":"caught","count":1},{"word":"explain","count":1},{"word":"skipping","count":1},{"word":"reason","count":1},{"word":"respect","count":1},{"word":"o-or","count":1},{"word":"teachers","count":1},{"word":"uh","count":1},{"word":"probe","count":1},{"word":"robots","count":1},{"word":"days","count":1},{"word":"ago","count":1},{"word":"sent","count":1},{"word":"measure","count":1},{"word":"voidmatter","count":1},{"word":"concentrations","count":1},{"word":"tundra","count":1},{"word":"thought","count":1},{"word":"finish","count":1},{"word":"collecting","count":1},{"word":"tried","count":1},{"word":"approach","count":1},{"word":"started","count":1},{"word":"attacking","count":1},{"word":"chased","count":1},{"word":"missed","count":1},{"word":"sorry","count":1},{"word":"great","count":1},{"word":"thanks","count":1},{"word":"anyway","count":1},{"word":"helping","count":1},{"word":"black","count":1},{"word":"robes","count":1},{"word":"gold","count":1},{"word":"embroidery","count":1},{"word":"wearing","count":1},{"word":"headpiece","count":1},{"word":"shaped","count":1},{"word":"two","count":1},{"word":"symbol","count":1},{"word":"exostrider","count":1},{"word":"shepherds","count":1},{"word":"shepherd","count":1},{"word":"robe","count":1},{"word":"someone","count":1},{"word":"higher","count":1},{"word":"solsworn","count":1},{"word":"powerful","count":1},{"word":"members","count":1},{"word":"tribe","count":1},{"word":"highest","count":1},{"word":"rank","count":1},{"word":"heard","count":1},{"word":"use","count":1},{"word":"heliogyre","count":1},{"word":"predict","count":1},{"word":"everything","count":1},{"word":"bird","count":1},{"word":"migrations","count":1},{"word":"void","count":1},{"word":"storms","count":1},{"word":"hard","count":1},{"word":"never","count":1},{"word":"leave","count":1},{"word":"surrounded","count":1},{"word":"light","count":1},{"word":"year","count":1},{"word":"round","count":1},{"word":"allowed","count":1},{"word":"enter","count":1},{"word":"try","count":1},{"word":"meeting","count":1},{"word":"unappointed","count":1},{"word":"sigrika","count":1},{"word":"currently","count":1},{"word":"researching","count":1},{"word":"frostlands","count":1},{"word":"around","count":1},{"word":"foreseer","count":1},{"word":"yngvar","count":1},{"word":"show","count":1},{"word":"able","count":1},{"word":"royan","count":1},{"word":"shepherdess","count":1},{"word":"atuja","count":1},{"word":"camp","count":1},{"word":"name's","count":1},{"word":"astrid","count":1},{"word":"better","count":1},{"word":"credits","count":1},{"word":"knew","count":1},{"word":"run","count":1},{"word":"into","count":1},{"word":"trouble","count":1},{"word":"asked","count":1},{"word":"robot","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Calm down, Maja, calm down... Good, they've stopped for now. Maybe I should just shut them down?","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"No, if I force the shutdown, I'll lose the data. Our thesis! Oh, somebody help!!","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"Huh? Professor Mornye?!","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"Oh no, I've been caught out of class! Wait, wait, let me explain! I wasn't skipping class! I'm here for a very good reason! It's not that I don't respect the class, o-or my teachers!","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"So, uh... can you just...","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"Well, these are probe robots from a few days ago. We sent them out to measure Voidmatter concentrations in the tundra.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"We thought we'd finish collecting the data before class, but when we tried to approach them, they started attacking us.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"I chased them all the way here. That's why I missed the class today...","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"I'm so sorry...","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"Great! Do you think the data...","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"What?!","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"But... Oh, well. Thanks anyway for helping out. Professor Mornye, and—","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"You want to find a Roya in black robes with gold embroidery, wearing a headpiece shaped like two horns?","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"The horns are a symbol of the Exostrider. <te href=700024>Shepherds</te> wear them, but no Shepherd would wear a robe like that...","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"Could be someone higher up. Like the <te href=700025>Solsworn</te> from the Solisylum, or even one of <te href=700020>the Heliodic Six</te>.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"That's right. They're the six most powerful members of the Roya tribe. The highest in rank, too.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"I've heard they use the Heliogyre to predict everything, from bird migrations to Void Storms. They know it all.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"Huh?! That might be hard.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"They never leave the <te href=700018>Solisylum</te>. It's surrounded by light all year round. Very few Roya are even allowed to enter.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"But maybe you could try meeting with one of the unappointed Heliodic Six?","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"Sigrika is currently out researching in the frostlands. The only other one around is Foreseer Yngvar, but he doesn't show himself much.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"If you want to find him, my mam might be able to help. She's a Royan Shepherdess over at Atuja camp. Name's Astrid.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002},{"text":"Now then, I'd better get back to my class before I lose all my credits. Who knew I'd run into trouble today? I even asked my mam to help me with the robot.","quest_name":"Ode to the Second Sunrise","quest_id":155000002}]}